 David Potchen , who robbed a bank in Merrillville , Indiana , last June , now has a job as a welder and is staying out of trouble after receiving help from family members .
The man , 53 , had told a Lake County judge that he attempted to rob a bank so he could get placed back in custody .
He is now employed and living with his relatives .
Potchen spent 12 and a half years in prison .